title: The Twilight Zone - Will The Real Martian Stand Up

Apparently one alien had walked away from the spot. They drive to the nearby highway CafÃƒÂ© and they find a bus with seven passengers waiting for the reopening of a snowed in bridge. When the passengers are released and the bus follows his travel, one passenger returns to the diner and discloses a plot of the invasion of the Earth
